quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  74,18,"O keefeero mbo neemin…óa …óiin neemaali o miiliima ko o wiyata e Quraana ngam bonnude mbo, o hoddiri …óuum e fittaandu makko."
  74,19,"O hu…óaama o lepta hono no o hoddiri."
  74,20,"Refti o hu…óa o lepta hono no o hoddiri."
  74,21,"Refti o ndaartandi ko o haalata."
  74,22,"Refti o √±ir…ìanii o …ìeydi √±ir…ìinaade, saanga nde o he…ìaani ko o yuwri Quraana o."
  74,23,"Refti o runtii iimaan, o mawnikinii rewde e Annabi-yo o his-."
  74,24,"O wi*i: Ko Muhamadu addi ko, wonah haala Alla, kono ko …óum mbilewu mbo o habrata ummaade wo…ì…ìe."
  74,25,"Ko haala wonah haala Alla, kono ko ka haala aade."
  74,26,"Ma Mi naatnu o keefeero be…ói be…ói yiite, ngeen woni Saqara o muuse nguleeki henge."
  74,27,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan muhamadu- ko woni yiite Saqara."
  74,28,"Nge heddatah hay huunde e leptatee…óe o singe arii e makko, nge accataa mbo haa o rutto no o laatarino nih, refti nge ara e makko kadi."
  74,29,"Sattunge sumgol e waylude guri."
  74,30,"Ina e dow mannge sappo e jeenay malayka, ko …ìeen ngoni reenoo…ìe nge."
  74,31,"Men wa…óaali aynoo…ìe Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ikaa…ìe, tawde ne…ó…óo waawaa …óum. Abu Jahal fenuno fewndo o aa∆¥inoo wiide kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen …ìe waaway dartagol …ìen Malaa'ikaa…ìe haa …ìe fuutoo e Yiite ngen. Hary non, Men wa…óiraali limoore …ìen, si wanaa jarribagol yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen, fii no …ìe wowolira haala kan haala ma…ì…ìe, lette …óen sowanee …ìe, e fii no Alyaahuda yim…ìe Tawreeta'en e Annasaara yim…ìe Linnjiila'en fellitira fewndo jippagol Alqur'aana, wonnde ko nde goonginnde ko woni e Defte ma…ì…ìe …óen, e fii no gom…óim…ìe …ìen …ìeydora gom…óinal tuma yim…ìe Defte …ìen fottata e ma…ì…ìe, e fii wata Alyahuuda e Annasaara e gom…óim…ìe sikkito, e fii no murtu…ìe e gom…óinal …ìen e heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ira : hara ko hon…óum Allah faandorii e ndee limooore haawniide? Ko wano …ìee yeddu…ìe ndee limoore majjinri non, goongim…ìe …ìen feewiri …óum, Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani majjugol, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani feewugol. Hay gooto anndaa no koneeli Joomi maa …óin fotata e …óuu…óude, si wanaa Kanko tun. Yo Abu Jahal anndi …óum, wi'unoo…óo : Muhamaadu alaa walloo…ìe si wanaa sappo e jeenay? O lamndori …óum jalkitugol fenna. Haray ngen Yiite wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde ne…ó…óanke, fii ko o anndira mawngu Allah ngun."
  74,32,"Yo henane wanaa no yoga e sirkoo…ìe …ìen aa∆¥ori non woniri, wonnde wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe waawanay halfinaa…ìe Yiite ngen fii no …ìe fuutora. Allah woondirii lewru ndun."
  74,33,"O woondiri jemma si mbo runtiima."
  74,34,"O woondiri subaka si mbo jalbii."
  74,35,"Ko pellet, Yiite Jahannama ngen, ko jeyaange e musiibaaji maw…ói."
  74,36,"Ko nge jertinirnge e hul…ìinirnge yim…ìe …ìen."
  74,37,"Wonannde yi…óu…óo woo e mo'on onon yim…ìe …ìen, nde o yaccotoo e gom…óingol Allah golla ko mo∆¥∆¥i, maa o nennora keeferaaku e geddi."
  74,38,"Wonkii kala ko fagiikon e golle nanngirte, Ko si tawii golle makki halkay fii makki, maa si tawii hara …óe da…ónday ki."
  74,39,"Si wanaa gom…óim…ìe …ìen, …ìen …óon nanngitiroytaake goopi mun, …ìe yawtanoyte …óin, sabu golle ma…ì…ìe mo∆¥∆¥e …óen."
  74,40,"∆Åe wonoyay √ëalnde Darngal e nder geese, hara hi…ìe lamndondira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe."
  74,41,"Fii heefer…ìe halkir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen golle geddi."
  74,42,"∆Åe wi'ana …ìen : ko hon…óum naadi on Jahannama?"
  74,43,"Heefer…ìe …ìen jaaboo …ìe : men jeyanooka e juulaynoo…ìe farlaa…óe …óen e nguurndam aduna."
  74,44,"Men jeyanooka kadi e √±amminaynoo…ìe waas…ìe …ìen e ko Allah ye…ói men kon."
  74,45,"Hari kadi ko yim…ìe meere …ìen min yiiladaynoo e mun, men yewtida e majju…ìe bew…ìe …ìen."
  74,46,"Hari kadi men fennayno fii √±alaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe nden."
  74,47,"Men woni e fennugol …óum, haa maayde nden arani men, men ronkii tuubude."